<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Title of article. (Year of publication). <em>Title of Publication, volume</em>(issue), 
	page numbers. doi:Digital Object Identifier (if assigned)
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Title of article">Study smarter, not harder: Setting goals to improve your academic performance</span>. 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>).&nbsp;
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Publication">Student Review</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="volume">25</span></em>(<span class="hover" title="issue">5</span>),  
	<span class="hover" title="page numbers">10&#45;12</span>. 
	doi:<span class="hover" title="Digital Object Identifier">12.3456789012</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
